title: Duke Engineering Master's Hooding Ceremony - BME, CEE, MEMS & Professional Programs - 2022

media:group.media:title: Duke Engineering Master's Hooding Ceremony - BME, CEE, MEMS & Professional Programs - 2022
media:group.media:description:
Class of 2022 Graduates in Duke's Master of Engineering and Master of Science programs in AI for Product Innovation, Biomedical Engineering, Civil & Environmental Engineering, Financial Technology,  and Mechanical Engineering & Materials Science, and master's degree graduates of the Duke University Program in Materials Science & Engineering, were celebrated and recognized during a ceremony held at 10 a.m. ET, Saturday, May 7 in Reynolds Industries Theater on the campus of Duke University.
More: https://pratt.duke.edu/about/news/duke-engineering-celebrates-class-2022
